{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CustomEvent","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document_Object_Model\">Document Object Model</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent/detail\"><code>detail</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent/initCustomEvent\"><code>initCustomEvent()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for DOM</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AbortController\"><code>AbortController</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AbortSignal\"><code>AbortSignal</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange\"><code>AbstractRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Attr\"><code>Attr</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CDATASection\"><code>CDATASection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CharacterData\"><code>CharacterData</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Comment\"><code>Comment</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMError\"><code>DOMError</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMImplementation\"><code>DOMImplementation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMParser\"><code>DOMParser</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPointReadOnly\"><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><code>CustomEvent&nbsp;</code>事件是由程序创建的，可以有任意自定义功能的事件。</p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> 此特性在 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Worker</a> 中可用</p>\n</div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"构造函数","title":"构造函数","isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent/CustomEvent\" title=\"CustomEvent()\"><code>CustomEvent()</code></a> &nbsp;</strong>创建一个自定义事件。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent/detail\"><code>CustomEvent.detail</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span> 任何时间初始化时传入的数据</strong></p>\n\n<p><em>此接口从父接口继承属性，&nbsp;</em><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a>：</p>\n\n<p>{{Page(\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\", \"Properties\")}}</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"customevent.initcustomevent\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent/initCustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent.initCustomEvent()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>\n <p>初始化一个 <code>CustomEvent 对象。如果事件已经被触发，这个方法将不会起任何作用。</code></p>\n </dd>\n</dl>\n\n<p><em>此接口从父接口继承方法，&nbsp;</em><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a>：</p>\n\n<p>{{Page(\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\", \"Methods\")}}</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"method_overview","title":"方法概述","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>void <a href=\"#initcustomevent()\">initCustomEvent</a>(in DOMString type, in boolean canBubble, in boolean cancelable, in any detail);</code></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attributes","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>属性</th>\n   <th>类型</th>\n   <th>描述</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>detail</code></td>\n   <td><code>any</code></td>\n   <td>当事件初始化时传递的数据。</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"initcustomevent()","title":"initCustomEvent()","isH3":true,"content":"<p>初始化一个自定义事件的方式和初始化一个标准 DOM 事件的方式非常相似。</p>\n\n<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">void initCustomEvent(\n  in DOMString type,\n  in boolean canBubble,\n  in boolean cancelable,\n  in any detail\n);\n</pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"parameters\">参数</h4>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"type\"><code>type</code></dt>\n <dd>事件的类型名称。</dd>\n <dt id=\"canbubble\"><code>canBubble</code></dt>\n <dd>一个布尔值，表明该事件是否会冒泡。</dd>\n <dt id=\"cancelable\"><code>cancelable</code></dt>\n <dd>一个布尔值，表明该事件是否可以被取消。</dd>\n <dt id=\"detail\"><code>detail</code></dt>\n <dd>当事件初始化时传递的数据。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"构造函数_2","title":"构造函数","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://dvcs.w3.org/hg/domcore/raw-file/tip/Overview.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM4 规范</a> 添加了对 <code>CustomEvent</code> 构造函数的支持。</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">CustomEvent(\n  DOMString type,\n  optional CustomEventInit eventInitDict\n)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"type_2\"><code>type</code></dt>\n <dd>事件的类型名称。</dd>\n <dt id=\"eventinitdict\"><code>eventInitDict</code></dt>\n <dd>一个提供事件的配置信息对象。查看<a href=\"#customeventinit\">CustomEventInit</a>了解更多详情。</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<h4 id=\"customeventinit\">CustomEventInit</h4>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"bubbles\"><code>bubbles</code></dt>\n <dd>一个布尔值，表明该事件是否会冒泡。</dd>\n <dt id=\"cancelable_2\"><code>cancelable</code></dt>\n <dd>一个布尔值，表明该事件是否可以被取消。</dd>\n <dt id=\"detail_2\"><code>detail</code></dt>\n <dd>当事件初始化时传递的数据。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"customevent_example_usage","title":"CustomEvent 用法示例","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// 添加一个适当的事件监听器</span>\nobj<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"cat\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token function\">process</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>detail<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 创建并分发事件</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> event <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">CustomEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"cat\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string-property property\">\"detail\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string-property property\">\"hazcheeseburger\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nobj<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">dispatchEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"specification","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#interface-customevent","title":"DOM Standard"}],"query":"api.CustomEvent"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.CustomEvent","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"构造函数","id":"构造函数"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"方法概述","id":"method_overview"},{"text":"属性","id":"attributes"},{"text":"方法","id":"methods"},{"text":"构造函数","id":"构造函数_2"},{"text":"规范","id":"specification"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"CustomEvent 事件是由程序创建的，可以有任意自定义功能的事件。","popularity":0.0007,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CustomEvent","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CustomEvent","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"CustomEvent","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CustomEvent","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CustomEvent","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"CustomEvent","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/customevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/customevent/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent","title":"CustomEvent"}],"pageTitle":"CustomEvent - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}